g.text: Type options are kept to a few standardized variations. Type is optimized for
mobile display. On desktop, reducing sizes slightly may be appropriate.
The default font weight is regular. Semibold is used for headers, and Medium
sometimes for certain components that require a little more visual weight (like a
lower contrast button label on a flat shape).
Default line height is 140%.
Colors (mostly black and grey (#70) are also used to establish visual hierarchy.
